{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm working very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't have time to prepare myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I just want--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's one of the reasons why I was not able to get a, a higher rank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they, they, they look forward to-- I should be a captain, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I just felt very comfortable with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the pay was also very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had a-- we had a double pay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to pay us in, in rubles, and then-- in, in German marks-- in the occupation marks-- and then twice as much in rubles.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this family that-- I housed them in Kovno, I used to send them packages constantly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was that-- they were the only guy-- the only relatives that I had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was able to, to, to send them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, next to our compound, where we had-- and our investigative force was really very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went twice to Nuremberg with, with the colonel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to attest that, I have-- the only thing what I was able to, to save is I have a, a, a cigarette box, a plastic, with the inscription of Nuremberg, 1941-1945.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, I-- we went in as-- just then as, as observers, not, not as participants.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And plus the fact, my-- the, the colonel wanted to get a little bit certain ideas how to conduct the process of the Sachsenhausen crimes, you know, this concentration camp which we were investigating.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was quite interesting to be there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the two times, twice, that-- we were-- we were short.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not-- be able able to sit in the process too long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I accompanied him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was quite, quite-- experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
